body.description: Playtime is more fun when your kids can easily take out their toys, books and games and then quickly clean up afterwards. The space-saving Humble Crew Super Sized Toy Storage Organizer with 16 Storage Bins stows your children's toys in easy-to-see, easy-to-access BPA and phthalate free plastic storage bins. Stylish colorways make it ideal for organizing your child’s nursery, bedroom, playroom, closet, even the living room....the options are endless! The 12 standard and 4 large storage containers are easy to remove, replace and reposition along the 4 tiered shelves—sized just right within the toy organizer for toddlers and preschool-aged children. It makes a great toy box storage alternative, helping keep your little one’s room clean and organized while at the same time teaching sorting and cognitive skills. Made with a sturdy engineered wood construction frame and steel shelving rods, each level can hold up to 20 pounds. Some assembly is required and all hardware is included. Product sizing - 42"W x 11"D (16"D with stabilizing braces) x 32" H Standard bin sizing: 12" L x 9"W x 6" H Large bin sizing: 16"L x 12"W x 6"H Additional plastic storage toy bins are sold separately.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Furnish it. Organize it. Store it. Love it! Choose Humble Crew We're parents who design products for kids just like our own— naturally, safety is our #1 priority. We have millions of products in families' homes and each is tested to the highest standard. We started as the leading storage organizer brand, being the first manufacturer to produce Super Sized and Extra Large storage organizers. We've since expanded our product catalog to provide families with comprehensive solutions for kids furniture, storage and play spaces. To date, we've sold millions of items across our catalog in the 25 years we've been in business, with over 50,000 reviews and an average 4.5 star rating. We’re committed not only to making well-designed essentials for your home, but to making a difference. Our reputation as a company is built by focusing on creating products with a purpose: to turn homes into havens of comfort and style while helping make life better for others through our educational scholarships and charitable giving.
Made Just for Kids Just the right height for children to identify, retrieve and put away their toys all on their own.

Features to Love Rounded Corners We know accidents happen—that’s why all of the corners on our organizers are rounded. In case of a stumble, your child is protected from sharp edges that could hurt them. Stabilizing Braces & Anti-Tip Kit Safety for your children is our #1 priority. When your child take a bin out to play, we only want the bin to come down! Our 16 bin storage organizer includes stabilizing braces that keep the unit upright and sturdy. Anti-tip straps and hardware are also included to give you additional peace of mind. Certified BPA & Phthalate Free Our plastic bins never have BPA or Phthalates, so you can rest easy knowing your child isn't handling a harmful or dangerous product during playtime. Room for Everything 4 large bins and 12 small bins mean the organizational possibilities are endless! Large enough to hold stuffed animals, balls, toy trucks and more, you can get toys off of the ground and keep your space

Complete Your Room with the Humble Crew Inspire Collection Humble Crew Inspire Kids Book Rack Storage Bookshelf, 4 Tiers Kid-sized storage organizer stows your child's toys in easy-to-see, easy-to-access plastic storage bins to help keep their play space clean and tidy. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quick and easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my daughter's bedroom because I needed someplace for her to place her toys and keep her room organized. The size was slightly bigger than I expected, however, I was able to get it to fit neatly in her room, and it was light enough that I could build it in my room, and carry it into her room (As my room had more room). Once within the room, It was easy to place the bins in, and it was easy for them to move in and out to reorganize, and spacious enough that I could a majority of her toys in there.I do wish that it wasn't as bulky as it is to move around, but it is good quality and has helped massively at keeping her room organized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great if attached to wall
reviews.reviewText: The Humble Crew Supersized Wood Toy Storage Organizer has been a lifesaver in keeping my children’s play area tidy. Its extra-large size makes it perfect for storing a wide variety of toys.The organizer includes 12 standard size open storage plastic bins and 4 double size open storage plastic bins. These removable bins are great for playtime and cleanup. They’re durable, easy to clean, and easy to assemble.What I love about this organizer is its material. It’s made of wood, plastic, and metal, ensuring it can withstand the rough and tumble of everyday play. Plus, it’s BPA and phthalate-free, which gives me peace of mind knowing it’s safe for my children.One tip I’ve found helpful is to secure the organizer to the wall. This provides extra stability, especially if your kids are a little rough with it.In summary, the Humble Crew Supersized Wood Toy Storage Organizer is a practical and efficient solution for toy storage. It’s helped transform my children’s play area into an organized, clutter-free space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It was much nicer than I was expecting
reviews.reviewText: I had read through all the negative reviews on here of this one and other brands that are similar and was keeping my expectations low. The box arrived, dirty, scuffed, and gouged with a bent in corner, and I was expecting the worst. I opened it up and was shocked to find the unit was unscathed. It went together very quickly(literally the quickest piece of baby furniture I think I’ve ever assembled.) it seems sturdy and looks nice. None of my polypropylene buckets were damaged in any way, despite the fact that there is no packing material between them and the other boards in the box, apart from a very thin piece of bubble wrap.I would recommend this toy storage unit. I think it is a great value for the price. I am pleased to report there are no smells at all. It doesn’t have the green guard gold certification like the Delta one but I don’t see why not because nothing seems to be offgassing.
